			  </ul>
			</div>

			<h2 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; color: #e74c3c; letter-spacing: 1px; border-bottom: 3px solid #e74c3c; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">MOMENT BY MOMENT BREAKDOWN</h2>

			<div class="row g-4 mb-4">
			  <div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
				  <div class="card-body">
					<h4 style="color: #e74c3c;">Opening Salvo</h4>
					<p>As the first cyclist advocate began their presentation, AARBAA members started a synchronized throat-clearing that sounded suspiciously like booing. Passive-aggressive? Absolutely. Effective? Undeniably.</p>
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			  <div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
				  <div class="card-body">
