					<p>Our data analysts unleashed a barrage of statistical evidence so precise it made the cyclist lobbyists' proposed bike lane maps look like kindergarten finger paintings.</p>
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</div>

			<blockquote class="bg-danger text-white p-4 my-4" style="font-style: italic; position: relative;">
			  <div style="position: absolute; top: -15px; left: -15px; width: 50px; height: 50px; background-color: white; transform: rotate(45deg);"></div>
			  <p>"We didn't just attend the meeting. We <em>conquered</em> it."</p>
			  <footer class="text-white-50">- Sarah Johnson, AARBAA Strategic Commander</footer>
			</blockquote>

			<h2 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; color: #e74c3c; letter-spacing: 1px; border-bottom: 3px solid #e74c3c; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">VICTORY HIGHLIGHTS</h2>

			<ul class="list-unstyled">
			  <li class="mb-3">
