				<span class="badge bg-danger me-2">üèÜ</span> 
				Reduced proposed bike lane budget by 62%
			  </li>
			</ul>

			<div class="text-center my-5">
			  <a href="#join" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg px-5 py-3" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">REINFORCE OUR RANKS</a>
			</div>

			<div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert" style="border-left: 5px solid #721c24;">
