			</div>

			<p class="text-muted mt-4">Disclaimer: This is a satirical account of civic engagement. AARBAA promotes dialogue, not destruction. (But also, totally destruction.)</p>
		  </article>
		</div>
	  </div>
	</div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>